underlying_type.type_name: int (void *, const void *, apr_ssize_t, const void *)

type.type_name: int (*)(void *, const void *, int, const void *)
type.pointee_type_name: int (void *, const void *, int, const void *)

name: APR_POOL_IMPLEMENT_ACCESSOR
text:
APR_POOL_IMPLEMENT_ACCESSOR(type) \
    APR_DECLARE(apr_pool_t *) apr_##type##_pool_get \
            (const apr_##type##_t *the##type) \
        { return the##type->pool; }

name: apr_pool_create
text:
apr_pool_create(newpool, parent) \
    apr_pool_create_ex(newpool, parent, NULL, NULL)

name: APR_RING_ENTRY
APR_RING_HEAD
APR_RING_SENTINEL
text:
APR_RING_SENTINEL(hp, elem, link)				\
    (struct elem *)((char *)(&(hp)->next) - APR_OFFSETOF(struct elem, link))

name: APR_RING_INIT
text:
APR_RING_INIT(hp, elem, link) do {				\
	APR_RING_FIRST((hp)) = APR_RING_SENTINEL((hp), elem, link);	\
	APR_RING_LAST((hp))  = APR_RING_SENTINEL((hp), elem, link);	\
    } while (0)

/

name: APR_RING_EMPTY
text:
APR_RING_EMPTY(hp, elem, link)					\
    (APR_RING_FIRST((hp)) == APR_RING_SENTINEL((hp), elem, link))

name: APR_RING_ELEM_INIT
text:
APR_RING_ELEM_INIT(ep, link) do {				\
	APR_RING_NEXT((ep), link) = (ep);				\
	APR_RING_PREV((ep), link) = (ep);				\
    } while (0)

name: APR_RING_SPLICE_BEFORE
text:
APR_RING_SPLICE_BEFORE(lep, ep1, epN, link) do {		\
	APR_RING_NEXT((epN), link) = (lep);				\
	APR_RING_PREV((ep1), link) = APR_RING_PREV((lep), link);	\
	APR_RING_NEXT(APR_RING_PREV((lep), link), link) = (ep1);	\
	APR_RING_PREV((lep), link) = (epN);				\
    } while (0)

/**

name: APR_RING_SPLICE_AFTER
text:
APR_RING_SPLICE_AFTER(lep, ep1, epN, link) do {			\
	APR_RING_PREV((ep1), link) = (lep);				\
	APR_RING_NEXT((epN), link) = APR_RING_NEXT((lep), link);	\
	APR_RING_PREV(APR_RING_NEXT((lep), link), link) = (epN);	\
	APR_RING_NEXT((lep), link) = (ep1);				\
    } while (0)

/**

name: APR_RING_SPLICE_HEAD
text:
APR_RING_SPLICE_HEAD(hp, ep1, epN, elem, link)			\
	APR_RING_SPLICE_AFTER(APR_RING_SENTINEL((hp), elem, link),	\
			     (ep1), (epN), link)

name: APR_RING_SPLICE_TAIL
text:
APR_RING_SPLICE_TAIL(hp, ep1, epN, elem, link)			\
	APR_RING_SPLICE_BEFORE(APR_RING_SENTINEL((hp), elem, link),	\
			     (ep1), (epN), link)

name: APR_RING_INSERT_HEAD
text:
APR_RING_INSERT_HEAD(hp, nep, elem, link)			\
	APR_RING_SPLICE_HEAD((hp), (nep), (nep), elem, link)

name: APR_RING_INSERT_TAIL
text:
APR_RING_INSERT_TAIL(hp, nep, elem, link)			\
	APR_RING_SPLICE_TAIL((hp), (nep), (nep), elem, link)

name: APR_RING_CONCAT
APR_RING_PREPEND
APR_RING_UNSPLICE
text:
APR_RING_UNSPLICE(ep1, epN, link) do {				\
	APR_RING_NEXT(APR_RING_PREV((ep1), link), link) =		\
		     APR_RING_NEXT((epN), link);			\
	APR_RING_PREV(APR_RING_NEXT((epN), link), link) =		\
		     APR_RING_PREV((ep1), link);			\
    } while (0)

/**

name: APR_RING_FOREACH
text:
APR_RING_FOREACH(ep, head, elem, link)                          \
    for (ep = APR_RING_FIRST(head);                                     \
         ep != APR_RING_SENTINEL(head, elem, link);                     \
         ep = APR_RING_NEXT(ep, link))

/

name: APR_RING_FOREACH_SAFE
text:
APR_RING_FOREACH_SAFE(ep1, ep2, head, elem, link)               \
    for (ep1 = APR_RING_FIRST(head), ep2 = APR_RING_NEXT(ep1, link);    \
         ep1 != APR_RING_SENTINEL(head, elem, link);                    \
         ep1 = ep2, ep2 = APR_RING_NEXT(ep1, link))

/

name: APR_VERSION_AT_LEAST
text:
APR_VERSION_AT_LEAST(major,minor,patch)                    \
(((major) < APR_MAJOR_VERSION)                                     \
 || ((major) == APR_MAJOR_VERSION && (minor) < APR_MINOR_VERSION) \
 || ((major) == APR_MAJOR_VERSION && (minor) == APR_MINOR_VERSION && (patch) <= APR_PATCH_VERSION))

     && (*(const apr_uint32_t *)(const void *)(&(a)->s6_addr[8]) == ntohl(0x0000ffff)))
